          <li>✅ “set a reminder for tomorrow at 11 am to email boss”</li>
          <li>✅ “in 30 minutes take a break”</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="mode">
        <div style="font-size: 2.8rem;">⌨️</div>
