      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question">🔄 Can I set recurring reminders?</div><p>Absolutely. Just say or type “remind me every day at 9 AM to stretch” or “every Monday at 10 AM for team stand-up”. Recurring habits and meetings are fully supported.</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question">🗑️ What happens if I uninstall the extension?</div><p>All local data is erased automatically. If you used Google Calendar sync, those reminders stay in your calendar (you can delete them there).</p></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-question">⚡ Does it slow down my browser?</div><p>No. Set a Reminder is lightweight (~900KB) and uses minimal resources. Notifications and background sync are optimized for speed.</p></div>
